    "abstract": "<jats:title>Abstract</jats:title>\n                <jats:p>The role of temperature in Covid 19 pandemic has been subjected to frequent review. An effort was made to find out such relations from three districts in India. Data were analyzed for 14 weeks. It appears that temperature could impact the spread of the pandemic.</jats:p>",
